[[File:CloakingDevice-NEGWT.png|thumb|right|200px|[[Sienar Design Systems/Legends|Sienar Design Systems]] Prototype cloak field generator.]]
The '''Prototype cloak field generator''' was alleged to have been created by [[Sienar Design Systems/Legends|Sienar Design Systems]] for use only [[Darth Maul/Legends|Darth Maul's]] [[Scimitar/Legends|''Scimitar'']]. Powered by [[Stygium/Legends|stygium]] [[Crystal/Legends|crystals]], this [[Cloaking device/Legends|cloaking device]] allowed Maul to easily infiltrate virtually any [[Planet/Legends|world]] undetected. Unfortunately, the supply of stygium was limited by the lack of supply&mdash;the crystal could only be found on [[Aeten II/Legends|Aeten II]] and it had a frequent burnout rate. The components of the prototype cloak field generator included a computer core, cloaking field antenna, orbital thrusters, cloaking field matrix, power conduits, and power cells.

